<plot>Centered around a chase through San Francisco, three young-men have to battle inner-demons when Freedom decides to follow his heart and escape his criminal-life with his girlfriend, Angel. The chase begins on foot through back-alleys and quickly turns into a high-speed shoot-out in performance-cars, motorcycles and planes through the crooked-streets, country-roads and blue-skies of Northern California, finally culminating in a boat-chase through a chain of mountain-lakes.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?156407</url></doc>
